cz.syntea.xdef.component

Interface XComponent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XCTextComponent

    public interface XComponent
    Interface of XComponent (Java class generated from X-definitions according to a model of Element). Java source of the XComponent is possible to generate by GenXComponent.
